Geraldine Wall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geraldine_Wall 0 Geraldine Wall (June 24, 1912 – June 22, 1970) was an American actress who had numerous stage, film and television credits. Her career involved mainly character roles but encompassed a wide range of roles.
